00:12:09,766 --> 00:12:11,216
Stanley juga.

238
00:12:11,822 --> 00:12:13,085
Oh, hai, Stanley.

239
00:12:13,855 --> 00:12:15,728
Kalian istirahatlah, oke?

240
00:12:15,728 --> 00:12:17,122
Jangan khawatirkan apapun.

241
